{"tid":1085630,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益 點樣可以令個朋友戒賭","createTime":"2019-03-31T09:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T10:40:15.000Z","uid":215574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"792b6ff82585b1eb4ed9f28b2a5bab3c182b287c","tid":1085630,"uid":215574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T09:53:06.000Z","msg":"我有個朋友 本身只係會買下6合彩20蚊電腦飛<br />\n<br />\n有一排佢問我有冇買下馬仔同波 我同佢講我唔賭錢<br />\n<br />\n早幾日佢同我講話第一次買左馬仔 一場輸一場贏 回左本<br />\n<br />\n之後佢好有自信咁話有個計劃 話研究左數據 有發達大計<br />\n<br />\n我心諗 你玩左幾月馬仔就咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我叫佢講黎聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢話佢個玩法係買單T 一隻膽拖十隻腳 我問佢咁買要幾錢<br />\n<br />\n佢話咪10蚊一隻腳 有機會贏過千<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我聽完黑人問號 一場得10幾隻馬 你已經買左咁多隻咪贏硬<br />\n<br />\n之後佢去左馬會買飛 本身想買5場 <br />\n<br />\n點知出飛果個同佢講頭兩張已經過千 問佢繼唔繼續 <br />\n<br />\n佢當堂呆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />事後佢WhatsApp我話中撚左伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後果2場馬係今日開 一輸一贏 贏左一舊幾水 <br />\n<br />\n之後仲話下星期3再買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩方法令到佢戒賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ad5913d1ca0ac7f83fe6704e9f71e230437957","tid":1085630,"uid":215574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T10:40:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}